<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_2f2057b3-08d4-42e0-bd0d-74e42b8d52dc" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>E2D12</sptc><title id="_c6ca094f-6d05-49a1-b2d0-f517b6f99967">Class 7a buildings</title><archive-num/><subclause id="_465b1dfc-74d4-4c72-ba00-008cc179937e" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_8a7d7250-5b4d-4562-a1cb-b2e2bcb14cd3">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>In a Class 7a building, including a basement, provided with a mechanical ventilation system in accordance with AS 1668.2, the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1213_1.0.0.xml#_1b0c2237-d3d4-4981-97b8-209936e55520" id="_13fa9c88-594f-4ac3-9d5b-ff4f65d29b68" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">carpark</xref> ventilation system must be designed and installed as a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1213_1.0.0.xml#_1b0c2237-d3d4-4981-97b8-209936e55520" id="_06dd33e7-56a7-4b28-8430-881eba9601ec" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">carpark</xref> ventilation system in accordance with AS 1668.1.</p></subclause></clause>